  <entry>
    <title>搭建个人博客心得</title>
    <url>/2023/05/01/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h3><ol>
<li>Git<blockquote>
<p>在其 <strong><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">官网</a></strong> 上进行下载即可，代替windows自带的cmd。</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>Node.js<blockquote>
<p>在其 <strong><a href="https://nodejs.org/en">官网</a></strong> 进行下载即可。</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li>安装hexo <span id="more"></span><br>先创建一个文件夹，用于存放hexo，这也是以后博客存放资料和修改的地方，例如下面我创建了<code>D:\blog\myblog</code>的文件夹，<br>然后再右键，git bash here，(此处和cmd，再cd到此文件夹效果相同)，运行如下命令：<figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-<span class="keyword">cli</span> -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
然后可以用如下命令检查是否安装成功<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
若发现myblog下 <strong>node_modules</strong> 文件夹丢失，可运行如下命令重生成：<figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-<span class="keyword">cli</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<p>下面为试验区：</p>
<p>运行如下代码：</p>
<p>首先需要声明一下语言：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>例如” <code>python ...   </code>之类的。代码块还需要缩进四个字符。</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> a&gt;<span class="number">0</span> :</span><br><span class="line">    a = a-<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(a)   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>看看效果咋样。</p>
]]></content>
